						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/China-sets-up-30-million-Africa-food-fund-to-be-administered-by-FAO" title="China sets up $30 million Africa food fund to be administered by FAO" alt="link">China sets up $30 million Africa food fund to be administered by FAO</a></h2>

	
					<p>China has set up a 30 million dollar trust fund to back agricultural projects, mainly in Africa, carried out by the Food and Agriculture Organisation, the UN food agency has said. The money is aimed at helping developing countries to improve farming output with a view to achieving Millennium Development Goals, the Rome-based FAO said in a statement, adding that Beijing had joined the FAO's &quot;donor community&quot; with the agreement. (Source: African Agriculture, 26 March 2009)</p>
							<p><span class="date">17/04/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
